== About

I'm currently a final-year PhD student working with Prof.~[http://www.cse.cuhk.edu.hk/~byu/ Bei Yu]. 
Before joining CUHK, I received my Bachelor Degree of Integrated Circuit Design and Integrated Systems from
[http://www.tju.edu.cn Tianjin University].
My research interests
include VLSI CAD, Design for Manufacturability and Deep Learning. \[[http://appsrv.cse.cuhk.edu.hk/~hyyang/files/cv.pdf My Resume]\] \[[https://scholar.google.com.hk/citations?user=aTJ0RJUAAAAJ&hl=en Google Scholar]\]

